reviewText: I like this one we sold this one at a yard sale
I like this VHS. This is one of my favorites. It's funny, and from this childern can learn how to be healthy, and not to be afraid of doctors.

This video will help the most active toddler to 4 and 5 year told sit through an entire episode. My grandaughter is highly active at 3 and she loves it. There is stimulating activity in this video so a child will not get bored or loose interest.

This video is great because it features "Chicken Pops" and displays some of those great friendship moments where Tommy stands up for Chuckie. Since children nay have a lot of apprehension about going to the doctor, this particular video is good for starting discussion on being afraid of the doctor, taking medicine, and avoiding germs.
